Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说还真棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟有不少老油子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压制边境可不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有些地方没压制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这样子 马上又要轮到我们上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博格队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备完毕立刻出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个目标定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算换班了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 天气真的转冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 不是冷的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你珍藏的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被队长发现会挨骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在执行任务 交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真有那种混蛋老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神出奇好 专门找差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我之前的队长 光摆着一副架子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别有距高感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种队伍 还不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫时待命 移动目标可能有变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时是等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看作战会议上怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今天之内是定不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 这么冷的天要野管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 期间会维护神通的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有指令了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们几个?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机修组会依次过来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预定时间是23点整
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 没空睡觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21点整之前自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉喝酒都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到点前恢复清醒就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 挺···
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的口味好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家一直夸莉莉品味独特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算不上夸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 我要告诉你爸妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤儿院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道该不该这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有一对老夫妇收留了战争中的孤儿们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 希望送点礼物给孤儿院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉之前说错话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说错话?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没注意说了句「要告诉他爸妈」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以过去吗 虽然那里有点远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到点之前回来就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小礼物 以表心意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前还是敌人 可能不太好收吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们收下了 你们客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你们两个人照顾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始没打算照顾他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他们自己聚过来了 又不能放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在更像是他们在照顾我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能一直这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 阿妮娅和大家画的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨的时候 他们画着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅画···
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个孩子画的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算叫她画点别的 还是只画战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种世界成了她现在的日常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前不久我们还在攻击这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再凑近点看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出奥秘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是行家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起画画吧 大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 不能呆太久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再留一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去 记得留时间睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要通青维护了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了 你们猜猜是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你画了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想画这里的老爷爷和老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是别告诉他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然小孩无法理解莉莉的审美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:07:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请要要点心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到艾玛的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫艾玛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是你家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望那里永远都是孩子们的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是假设
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你现在觉得自己无处可归
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后一定会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前对遇见的孩子这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时这么说是想安慰她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也一直在寻找归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把我养大的家里 也没有归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方我们很难办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么意见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了生存才流落到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没把军队当自己的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 莉莉也觉得军队不是自己的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这支分队 大家在的地方就像归宿一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才盖尔队长说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「记得留时间睡觉 要通宵维护了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像呼嗦的爸爸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看布雷克兵曹长和盖伊那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时还挺温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然休伊是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总会有那么一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每家都有个头疼的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我以前就想要个帅气的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果斯黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也把这个分队当归宿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想拿这种表情糊弄过去 没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道该怎么回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手别停听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经决定下一个移动地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里往南120公里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在利奧·塔克拉斯州边上和强袭空母汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压制或破坏王国军设施
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来一个烫手山芋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6点30分出 发维护在两小时内结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你也把这个分队当归宿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.23,0:12:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到艾玛的家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是只会笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前也是这种孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样笑着就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样什么事都能忍过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续 继续 继续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往右一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机修组已经走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有办法的 大家先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计花一两个小时 我会追上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 你来帮忙 斯黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见 居然会犯这种错误
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 偶尔发现你像人的一面也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上 战场是最看得清人本性的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是硬派强壮的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了前线也会因恐惧吓得胆怯 哭喊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想像你一样保持平常心 都装不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有装
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为你抛弃了感情活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得自己变了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道这样子像不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后还能呆在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕很难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠这对老夫妇太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样的地方还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们能力有限
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总比什么都不做好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才开了孤儿院?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见那幅画了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的孤儿院里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会画战争血腥场景的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把孩子弄成那样的人就是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们有责任看到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让孩子们看到不同的世界 不同的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好好开车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是又发呆撞上了 我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉说过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长像个啰嗦的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧 我受够孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就到利奥·塔克拉斯州了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走了 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在掩体里打我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别退缩 应战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毁机枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走那边 走那块斜坡上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地雷 斜坡上埋了地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后退 别离开线路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 是想彻底挡住我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架势是坚决不让我们接近设施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那设施里到底有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能撤回去 舰炮射击要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会摧毁雷区的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 盖伊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好···
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是悬浮器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆一边喝酒去吧 剩下的交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了盖伊 那家伙关键时刻掉链子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉 身后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台机体···
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后退 要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护重要的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休伊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖伊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后替我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争结束 之后的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 安睡在我们面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索莱伊王国军身经百战的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗德·米勒骑士团总长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国皇帝开恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顾敌我关系 向您的死致以由衷的哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且静静收起汝向吾等亮出的利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛把敌人的葬礼办得这么隆重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是某种宣传吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣传？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟迟不完的战争 对方也一样累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要煽动对方的厌战情绪 瓦解他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有的人战死连具尸体都没留
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然队长不挑食
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但唯独不吃这个豆子料理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在执行任务 交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:15.05,标题,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1628,910)}{\fad(1000,1000)}「灵魂的发火」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(958,99)}你好 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(964,97)}现在安详地驾鹤归西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(964,97)}若非天时与立场将我们阻隔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(964,97)}怕是不会白刃相向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(964,97)}而是举杯共酌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(964,97)}畅谈各自效忠国家的未来
